Credit notice for hashbrown (SwissTable)
https://github.com/rust-lang/hashbrown

Algorithm reference for src/utils/swisstable.c3

The SwissTable implementation in Metaphor follows the algorithm design of
hashbrown, which is itself a Rust port of Google's SwissTable from the Abseil
C++ library. The C3 code was written from scratch but follows the same
algorithmic approach: SIMD group probing, H2 metadata bytes, and tombstone
compaction.

